### 1. 分页查询：第一页，每页5条
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/page?page=1&size=5
Accept: application/json

### 2. 分页 + 按考勤时间降序
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/page?page=1&size=5&sortBy=checkInTime&direction=desc
Accept: application/json

### 3. 分页 + 按学生ID升序
GET http://localhost:8085/attendance/page?page=2&size=5&sortBy=studentId&direction=asc
Accept: application/json

### 4. 条件查询：按学生ID
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 3,
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10
}

### 5. 条件查询：按课程ID
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10
}

### 6. 条件查询：按状态
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "LATE",
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10
}

### 7. 条件查询：按时间范围
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-04-01 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-04-30 23:59:59",
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10
}

### 8. 多条件组合查询
POST http://localhost:8085/attendance/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 3,
  "courseId": 1,
  "status": "NORMAL",
  "startTime": "2026-04-01 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-04-30 23:59:59",
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "sortBy": "checkInTime",
  "direction": "desc"
}